<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MenuLens — Accessible AI Menu Reader</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:#F2F2F7; --surface:rgba(255,255,255,0.78); --surface-2:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  --surface-3:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); --solid:#FFFFFF;
  --border:rgba(0,0,0,0.08); --border-2:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  --text:#1C1C1E; --text-2:#636366; --text-3:#AEAEB2;
  --blue:#007AFF; --blue-s:rgba(0,122,255,0.12);
  --green:#34C759; --green-s:rgba(52,199,89,0.12);
  --orange:#FF9500; --orange-s:rgba(255,149,0,0.12);
  --teal:#5AC8FA; --teal-s:rgba(90,200,250,0.14);
  --purple:#AF52DE; --purple-s:rgba(175,82,222,0.12);
  --red:#FF3B30; --red-s:rgba(255,59,48,0.10);
  --blur:blur(20px) saturate(180%);
  --r-sm:10px; --r-md:14px; --r-lg:20px; --r-xl:28px;
  --sh-sm:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06),0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --sh-md:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --sh-lg:0 8px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.10),0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  --spring:cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
  --ease:cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);
}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){:root{
  --bg:#000; --surface:rgba(28,28,30,0.82); --surface-2:rgba(44,44,46,0.72);
  --surface-3:rgba(58,58,60,0.62); --solid:#1C1C1E;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.10); --border-2:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  --text:#FFFFFF; --text-2:#AEAEB2; --text-3:#636366;
  --blue-s:rgba(0,122,255,0.18); --green-s:rgba(52,199,89,0.18);
  --orange-s:rgba(255,149,0,0.18); --teal-s:rgba(90,200,250,0.18);
  --purple-s:rgba(175,82,222,0.18); --red-s:rgba(255,59,48,0.16);
}}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;}
.app{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;min-height:100vh;}
@media(min-width:900px){.app{grid-template-columns:360px 1fr;}}
@media(min-width:1280px){.app{grid-template-columns:360px 1fr 340px;}}
.glass{background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);box-shadow:var(--sh-md);}
.glass-sm{background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-md);box-shadow:var(--sh-sm);}

/* HEADER */
.app-header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);padding:0 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:60px;grid-column:1/-1;}
.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.3px;}
.logo-mark{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:9px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue),var(--purple));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:0.95rem;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,122,255,0.3);}
.logo-text span{color:var(--blue);}
.tab-pills{display:flex;gap:4px;background:var(--surface-2);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:22px;padding:4px;}
.tab-pill{padding:6px 18px;border-radius:18px;border:none;font-family:inherit;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s var(--ease);color:var(--text-2);background:transparent;}
.tab-pill.active{background:var(--solid);color:var(--text);box-shadow:var(--sh-sm);font-weight:600;}
.live-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;background:var(--green-s);color:var(--green);border:0.5px solid rgba(52,199,89,0.25);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 12px;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;}
.live-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.4}}

/* COLUMNS */
.col-left{padding:1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;overflow-y:auto;height:calc(100vh - 60px);position:sticky;top:60px;}
.col-left::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}
.col-main{padding:1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;overflow-y:auto;border-left:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.col-right{padding:1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;overflow-y:auto;height:calc(100vh - 60px);position:sticky;top:60px;border-left:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.col-right::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:899px){
  .app{display:block;}
  .col-left,.col-main,.col-right{display:none;position:static;height:auto;border:none;padding-bottom:90px;}
  .col-left.mob-active,.col-main.mob-active,.col-right.mob-active{display:flex;}
  .app-header{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;}
  body{padding-top:60px;}
}

/* BOTTOM TAB BAR */
.btm-bar{display:none;position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:300;background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border-top:0.5px solid var(--border);padding:8px 0 20px;justify-content:space-around;align-items:center;}
@media(max-width:899px){.btm-bar{display:flex;}}
.btm-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;cursor:pointer;padding:4px 20px;border:none;background:none;font-family:inherit;}
.btm-icon{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;transition:transform 0.18s var(--spring);}
.btm-item.active .btm-icon{transform:scale(1.12);}
.btm-item:active .btm-icon{transform:scale(0.86);}
.btm-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-3);}
.btm-item.active .btm-label{color:var(--blue);font-weight:700;}

/* EYEBROW */
.eyebrow{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:0.6rem;}

/* HERO CARD */
.hero-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#007AFF 0%,#5856D6 100%);border-radius:var(--r-xl);padding:1.5rem;color:white;position:relative;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,122,255,0.32);cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.18s var(--spring),box-shadow 0.18s var(--ease);}
.hero-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(0,122,255,0.38);}
.hero-card:active{transform:scale(0.975);}
.hero-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-50px;right:-50px;width:200px;height:200px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:50%;}
.hero-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-70px;left:10px;width:160px;height:160px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border-radius:50%;}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0.7;margin-bottom:6px;}
.hero-title{font-size:1.45rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:4px;}
.hero-sub{font-size:0.82rem;opacity:0.75;margin-bottom:1.1rem;}
.hero-cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-radius:20px;padding:8px 18px;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;color:white;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.15s;}
.hero-cta:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);}

/* VENUE SWITCHER */
.venue-switcher{display:flex;gap:8px;}
.venue-btn{flex:1;padding:10px 8px;border-radius:var(--r-md);border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--text-2);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;transition:all 0.2s var(--spring);}
.venue-btn:hover{border-color:rgba(0,122,255,0.3);color:var(--blue);}
.venue-btn.active{background:var(--blue);border-color:var(--blue);color:white;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,122,255,0.3);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.venue-btn-emoji{font-size:1.2rem;}
.venue-btn-label{font-size:0.65rem;}

/* VENUE INTEL */
.venue-intel{border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--sh-md);}
.venue-intel-hero{padding:1.1rem 1.25rem 0.9rem;display:flex;gap:0.75rem;align-items:flex-start;}
.v-italian{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1A00,#5C3310);}
.v-pub{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0F2A1E,#1E5C3A);}
.v-french{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1A0A2E,#3D1F72);}
.venue-intel-icon{font-size:1.8rem;line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
.venue-intel-name{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);letter-spacing:-0.2px;line-height:1.2;}
.venue-intel-type{font-size:0.68rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:3px;font-weight:500;}
.venue-intel-body{background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-top:none;padding:1rem 1.25rem;}
.venue-summary{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:0.75rem;}
.venue-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;}
.venue-tag{font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue-s);border-radius:20px;padding:3px 10px;border:0.5px solid rgba(0,122,255,0.15);}
.venue-gf-alert{margin-top:0.75rem;padding:0.75rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--r-sm);font-size:0.76rem;line-height:1.55;font-weight:500;display:none;}
.venue-gf-alert.unsafe{background:var(--red-s);color:var(--red);border:0.5px solid rgba(255,59,48,0.2);}
.venue-gf-alert.caution{background:var(--orange-s);color:var(--orange);border:0.5px solid rgba(255,149,0,0.2);}
.venue-thinking{display:none;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;background:var(--surface-2);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-2);font-style:italic;}

/* MENU CHIPS */
.menu-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;}
.menu-chip{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.73rem;font-weight:500;border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-2);transition:all 0.18s var(--spring);font-family:inherit;}
.menu-chip:hover{border-color:rgba(255,149,0,0.4);color:var(--orange);}
.menu-chip.active{background:var(--orange);border-color:var(--orange);color:white;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(255,149,0,0.3);}

/* SETTINGS PANEL */
.settings-panel{padding:0.875rem 1rem;}
.setting-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border-2);font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text);}
.setting-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.ios-toggle{width:46px;height:27px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(120,120,128,0.16);position:relative;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:background 0.24s var(--ease);flex-shrink:0;}
.ios-toggle.on{background:var(--green);}
.ios-toggle::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:2px;left:2px;width:23px;height:23px;border-radius:50%;background:white;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);transition:transform 0.24s var(--ease);}
.ios-toggle.on::after{transform:translateX(19px);}
.font-ctrl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.font-btn{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:7px;border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface-2);font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-2);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.15s;}
.font-btn:hover{background:var(--blue);border-color:var(--blue);color:white;}
.font-val{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--text-3);min-width:22px;text-align:center;}

/* MENU DISPLAY */
.menu-display-header{padding:1.1rem 1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.restaurant-name{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:white;letter-spacing:-0.2px;}
.menu-cat-label{font-size:0.68rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:2px;font-weight:500;}
.menu-item-box{padding:1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-top:none;}
.menu-item-name{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.2px;margin-bottom:3px;}
.menu-item-price{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);}
.menu-item-desc{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;margin-top:8px;}
.dyslexia .menu-item-name{font-size:1.12rem;letter-spacing:0.02em;}
.dyslexia .menu-item-desc{font-size:0.92rem;line-height:1.95;letter-spacing:0.04em;word-spacing:0.15em;}

/* GF BANNER */
.gf-banner{border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:0.875rem 1rem;border:0.5px solid;}
.gf-banner.safe{background:var(--green-s);border-color:rgba(52,199,89,0.25);}
.gf-banner.unsafe{background:var(--red-s);border-color:rgba(255,59,48,0.22);}
.gf-banner.caution{background:var(--orange-s);border-color:rgba(255,149,0,0.22);}
.gf-banner-title{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;}
.gf-banner.safe .gf-banner-title{color:var(--green);}
.gf-banner.unsafe .gf-banner-title{color:var(--red);}
.gf-banner.caution .gf-banner-title{color:var(--orange);}
.gf-banner-body{font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.55;}
.gf-rec-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:8px;}
.gf-rec-chip{padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:600;background:var(--surface);border:0.5px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-2);transition:all 0.15s;font-family:inherit;}
.gf-rec-chip:hover{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:white;}

/* MOOD PICKER */
.mood-picker{display:flex;gap:8px;}
.mood-btn{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:14px 8px;border-radius:var(--r-md);border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all 0.2s var(--spring);}
.mood-btn:hover{border-color:rgba(255,149,0,0.35);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.mood-btn:active{transform:scale(0.94);}
.mood-btn.active{background:var(--orange);border-color:var(--orange);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(255,149,0,0.3);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.mood-emoji{font-size:1.5rem;line-height:1;}
.mood-label{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-2);}
.mood-btn.active .mood-label{color:white;}

/* REC CARD */
.rec-card{margin-top:0.75rem;border-radius:var(--r-md);overflow:hidden;border:0.5px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--sh-sm);animation:fadeUp 0.26s var(--spring);display:none;}
.rec-card.visible{display:block;}
.rec-card-head{padding:0.875rem 1rem;background:var(--surface-2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.rec-head-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.rec-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--surface);border:0.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.rec-meta-label{font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:2px;}
.rec-dish-name{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);}
.rec-close{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--text-3);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:0.7rem;transition:all 0.15s;font-family:inherit;}
.rec-close:hover{background:var(--red);border-color:var(--red);color:white;}
.rec-body{padding:0.875rem 1rem;background:var(--surface);}
.rec-desc{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:0.6rem;}
.rec-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;}
.rec-tag{padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:600;}
.tag-free{background:var(--green-s);color:var(--green);}
.tag-warn{background:var(--orange-s);color:var(--orange);}
.tag-note{background:var(--surface-2);color:var(--text-3);}

/* ACTION BUTTONS */
.action-row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.action-btn{flex:1;min-width:100px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:var(--r-md);border:0.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);font-family:inherit;font-size:0.76rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text-2);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:5px;transition:all 0.18s var(--spring);}
.action-btn:hover{border-color:rgba(0,122,255,0.3);color:var(--blue);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.action-btn:active{transform:scale(0.95);}
.action-btn.primary{background:var(--blue);border-color:var(--blue);color:white;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,122,255,0.28);}
.action-btn.primary:hover{box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,122,255,0.38);}

/* AI OUTPUT */
.ai-output{border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--sh-md);}
.ai-output-header{padding:0.875rem 1.1rem;background:var(--surface-2);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.ai-live-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
.ai-title{font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);flex:1;}
.ai-model-tag{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--text-3);background:var(--surface-2);border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px;border:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.ai-body{padding:1.1rem;background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);min-height:120px;}
.ai-placeholder{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:0.6rem;padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;color:var(--text-3);}
.ai-placeholder-icon{font-size:1.8rem;opacity:0.5;}
.ai-placeholder-text{font-size:0.76rem;line-height:1.6;max-width:260px;}
.ai-thinking{display:none;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:0.75rem;}
.ai-thinking.visible{display:flex;}
.thinking-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);animation:thinkBounce 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;}
.thinking-dot:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.2s;}.thinking-dot:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.4s;}
@keyframes thinkBounce{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:0.4}50%{transform:translateY(-6px);opacity:1}}
.thinking-text{font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--text-2);font-style:italic;}
.ai-result{display:none;}
.ai-result.visible{display:block;}
.result-name{font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.3px;margin-bottom:3px;}
.result-price{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:0.875rem;}
.result-desc{font-size:0.86rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--text-2);letter-spacing:0.01em;}
.result-allergens{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-top:0.875rem;}
.allergen-tag{padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:600;}
.allergen-tag.warn{background:var(--orange-s);color:var(--orange);border:0.5px solid rgba(255,149,0,0.25);}
.allergen-tag.free{background:var(--green-s);color:var(--green);border:0.5px solid rgba(52,199,89,0.25);}
.rword{border-radius:3px;transition:background 0.08s;}
.rword.lit{background:rgba(255,149,0,0.28);}

/* READ ALOUD */
.read-aloud-bar{margin-top:0.875rem;padding-top:0.875rem;border-top:0.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
.play-btn{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);border:none;color:white;font-size:0.85rem;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,122,255,0.28);transition:transform 0.18s var(--spring),box-shadow 0.15s;}
.play-btn:hover{transform:scale(1.08);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,122,255,0.38);}
.play-btn:active{transform:scale(0.9);}
.waveform{flex:1;height:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;}
.wave-bar{flex:1;border-radius:2px;background:var(--border);transition:height 0.12s,background 0.12s;}
.waveform.playing .wave-bar{background:var(--blue);animation:waveAnim 0.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;}
.wave-bar:nth-child(2n){animation-delay:0.1s;}.wave-bar:nth-child(3n){animation-delay:0.2s;}.wave-bar:nth-child(4n){animation-delay:0.3s;}
@keyframes waveAnim{from{height:4px}to{height:18px}}
.audio-meta{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;min-width:80px;}
.audio-label{font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--text-2);}
.auto-play-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:0.63rem;color:var(--text-3);cursor:pointer;}

/* CX ANALYTICS PANEL */
.analytics-title{font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.2px;}
.kpi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;}
.kpi-card{background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:0.875rem 1rem;cursor:default;transition:all 0.18s var(--spring);}
.kpi-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--sh-md);}
.kpi-label{font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.07em;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:6px;}
.kpi-value{font-size:1.45rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.3px;line-height:1;}
.kpi-delta{font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px;}
.delta-up{color:var(--green);}
.sentiment-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.1rem;background:var(--surface);backdrop-filter:var(--blur);-webkit-backdrop-filter:var(--blur);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:1rem;}
.ring-wrap{width:72px;height:72px;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;}
.ring-wrap svg{transform:rotate(-90deg);width:72px;height:72px;}
.ring-bg{fill:none;stroke:var(--border);stroke-width:7;}
.ring-fill{fill:none;stroke:var(--green);stroke-width:7;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-dasharray:188;stroke-dashoffset:38;}
.ring-label{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.ring-pct{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);line-height:1;}
.ring-sub{font-size:0.5rem;color:var(--text-3);font-weight:600;margin-top:1px;}
.sentiment-breakdown{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;flex:1;}
.sentiment-title{font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:5px;}
.sent-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--text-2);}
.sent-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;}
.friction-card{overflow:hidden;}
.friction-header{padding:0.875rem 1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.friction-header-title{font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);}
.friction-header-sub{font-size:0.63rem;color:var(--text-3);}
.friction-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:0.6rem 1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border-2);transition:background 0.15s;}
.friction-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.friction-item:hover{background:var(--surface-2);}
.friction-name{font-size:0.73rem;color:var(--text-2);flex:1;}
.friction-track{width:72px;height:5px;background:var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;}
.friction-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;}
.fill-high{background:var(--red);}
.fill-mid{background:var(--orange);}
.fill-low{background:var(--green);}
.friction-pct{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.66rem;color:var(--text-3);width:28px;text-align:right;}
.insight-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#34C759,#30B350);border-radius:var(--r-md);padding:1rem 1.1rem;color:white;}
.insight-eyebrow{font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;opacity:0.7;margin-bottom:4px;}
.insight-text{font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.6;}
.insight-text strong{font-weight:700;}
.journey-row{display:flex;padding:1rem;gap:0;align-items:flex-start;}
.journey-step{flex:1;text-align:center;position:relative;}
.journey-step::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:13px;left:50%;width:100%;height:1.5px;background:var(--border);z-index:0;}
.journey-step:last-child::after{display:none;}
.journey-dot-wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:5px;}
.journey-dot{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);}
.journey-dot.done{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:white;}
.journey-label{font-size:0.58rem;color:var(--text-3);line-height:1.3;font-weight:500;}

/* WORKFLOW */
.wf-steps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
.wf-step{display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;position:relative;padding-bottom:1.25rem;}
.wf-step:last-child{padding-bottom:0;}
.wf-step::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:19px;top:40px;width:1.5px;height:calc(100% - 12px);background:var(--border);}
.wf-step:last-child::before{display:none;}
.wf-icon-box{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:10px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;z-index:1;border:0.5px solid var(--border);}
.wf-capture{background:var(--orange-s);border-color:rgba(255,149,0,0.25);}
.wf-ai{background:var(--teal-s);border-color:rgba(90,200,250,0.25);}
.wf-render{background:var(--red-s);border-color:rgba(255,59,48,0.2);}
.wf-voice{background:var(--purple-s);border-color:rgba(175,82,222,0.2);}
.wf-analytics{background:var(--blue-s);border-color:rgba(0,122,255,0.2);}
.wf-name{font-size:0.83rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:3px;}
.wf-desc{font-size:0.74rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.55;}
.wf-tech{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;margin-top:5px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--text-3);background:var(--surface-2);border-radius:4px;padding:2px 8px;}

/* ANALYTICS TAB */
.friction-word-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;}
.fw-chip{padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) scale(0.98)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="app-header">
  <a class="logo" href="#">
    <div class="logo-mark">🔍</div>
    <div class="logo-text">Menu<span>Lens</span></div>
  </a>
  <div class="tab-pills">
    <button class="tab-pill active" onclick="switchMainTab('demo',this)">Live Demo</button>
    <button class="tab-pill" onclick="switchMainTab('workflow',this)">AI Workflow</button>
    <button class="tab-pill" onclick="switchMainTab('analytics',this)">CX Analytics</button>
  </div>
  <div class="live-badge"><div class="live-dot"></div>AI-Powered</div>
</header>

<div class="app">

<!-- ══ LEFT COLUMN ══ -->
<div class="col-left mob-active" id="colLeft">

  <div id="tab-demo">
    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">AI Menu Accessibility</div>
      <div class="hero-title">Read any menu with confidence</div>
      <div class="hero-sub">Dyslexia-friendly · GF mode · Read aloud · 3 venues</div>
      <div class="hero-cta">Get started ›</div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Switch Restaurant</div>
      <div class="venue-switcher">
        <button class="venue-btn active" onclick="switchVenue(0,this)"><span class="venue-btn-emoji">🍝</span><span class="venue-btn-label">Italian</span></button>
        <button class="venue-btn" onclick="switchVenue(1,this)"><span class="venue-btn-emoji">🍺</span><span class="venue-btn-label">Pub</span></button>
        <button class="venue-btn" onclick="switchVenue(2,this)"><span class="venue-btn-emoji">🥂</span><span class="venue-btn-label">French</span></button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Venue Intelligence <span style="font-size:0.55rem;background:var(--teal-s);color:var(--teal);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.05em;vertical-align:middle">AI</span></div>
      <div id="venueThinking" class="venue-thinking"><div class="thinking-dot"></div><div class="thinking-dot"></div><div class="thinking-dot"></div><span style="font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--text-2);font-style:italic">Analysing restaurant…</span></div>
      <div class="venue-intel" id="venueIntelCard">
        <div class="venue-intel-hero v-italian" id="venueHeroBg">
          <div class="venue-intel-icon" id="venueIcon">🍝</div>
          <div><div class="venue-intel-name" id="venueName">La Trattoria Bella</div><div class="venue-intel-type" id="venueType">🇮🇹 Italian · Fine Dining · Seasonal Menu</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="venue-intel-body">
          <div class="venue-summary" id="venueSummary">This is an Italian restaurant — <strong>expect pasta to be the star of the show.</strong> Most dishes are built around wheat-based noodles, risotto, or bread. Starters lean on cured meats, cheeses, and bruschetta.</div>
          <div class="venue-tags" id="venueTags"><span class="venue-tag">🍝 Pasta-heavy</span><span class="venue-tag">🧀 Lots of dairy</span><span class="venue-tag">🥩 Meat mains</span><span class="venue-tag">🍷 Wine pairings</span></div>
          <div class="venue-gf-alert" id="venueGfAlert"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Choose a Menu Item</div>
      <div class="menu-chips" id="menuChips">
        <button class="menu-chip active" onclick="selectItem(0,this)">🍝 Pappardelle al Cinghiale</button>
        <button class="menu-chip" onclick="selectItem(1,this)">🥗 Salade Niçoise</button>
        <button class="menu-chip" onclick="selectItem(2,this)">🍖 Boeuf Bourguignon</button>
        <button class="menu-chip" onclick="selectItem(3,this)">🍮 Crème Brûlée</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Display Settings</div>
      <div class="glass-sm">
        <div class="settings-panel">
          <div class="setting-row"><span>Dyslexia-Friendly Font</span><button class="ios-toggle on" id="dyslexiaToggle" onclick="toggleDyslexia(this)"></button></div>
          <div class="setting-row"><span>🌾 Gluten-Free Mode</span><button class="ios-toggle" id="gfToggle" onclick="toggleGlutenFree(this)"></button></div>
          <div class="setting-row"><span>High Contrast</span><button class="ios-toggle" onclick="this.classList.toggle('on');document.body.style.filter=this.classList.contains('on')?'contrast(1.15)':''"></button></div>
          <div class="setting-row"><span>Word Highlighting</span><button class="ios-toggle" id="highlightToggle" onclick="this.classList.toggle('on');toggleHighlight(this)"></button></div>
          <div class="setting-row"><span>Font Size</span><div class="font-ctrl"><button class="font-btn" onclick="changeFontSize(-1)">−</button><div class="font-val" id="fontSizeDisplay">M</div><button class="font-btn" onclick="changeFontSize(1)">+</button></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="tab-workflow" style="display:none">
    <div class="glass" style="padding:1.25rem">
      <div style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.2px;margin-bottom:4px">MenuLens AI Workflow</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.25rem">A real-time accessibility pipeline powered by Claude Sonnet 4 — sitting between confusing menus and the 1 in 5 people with dyslexia.</div>
      <div class="wf-steps">
        <div class="wf-step"><div class="wf-icon-box wf-capture">📷</div><div><div class="wf-name">1 · Menu Capture</div><div class="wf-desc">Guest scans physical menu via camera, or restaurant pushes digital menu via SDK. Text extracted via OCR or passed directly.</div><div class="wf-tech">📱 Camera API · Tesseract OCR</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf-step"><div class="wf-icon-box wf-ai">🤖</div><div><div class="wf-name">2 · Claude Simplification</div><div class="wf-desc">Each item sent to Claude Sonnet 4 with a prompt tuned for dyslexia-friendly output: short sentences, plain words, no culinary jargon. Allergens parsed simultaneously.</div><div class="wf-tech">⚡ Anthropic API · claude-sonnet-4</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf-step"><div class="wf-icon-box wf-render">🖼️</div><div><div class="wf-name">3 · Accessible Rendering</div><div class="wf-desc">Output rendered using Inter typeface, wider spacing, WCAG AA+ contrast, adjustable font scale, and color-coded allergen tags.</div><div class="wf-tech">🎨 Inter · WCAG 2.1 AA</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf-step"><div class="wf-icon-box wf-voice">🔊</div><div><div class="wf-name">4 · Text-to-Speech</div><div class="wf-desc">Simplified text read aloud with word-by-word highlighting. Guests can listen without reading at all.</div><div class="wf-tech">🗣️ Web Speech API · ElevenLabs</div></div></div>
        <div class="wf-step"><div class="wf-icon-box wf-analytics">📊</div><div><div class="wf-name">5 · CX Analytics Loop</div><div class="wf-desc">Every interaction logged anonymously. Dashboard surfaces friction points, satisfaction trends, and accessibility ROI for restaurant operators.</div><div class="wf-tech">📈 Event stream · Segment · Dashboard</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="glass" style="padding:1.25rem"><div style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">The CX Problem</div><div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.7">Dyslexia affects ~15–20% of the population. A complex menu creates: <strong style="color:var(--text)">cognitive overload → anxiety → ordering the "safe" familiar dish → lower spend → lower satisfaction.</strong> MenuLens breaks that loop.</div></div>
  </div>

  <div id="tab-analytics-left" style="display:none">
    <div class="glass" style="padding:1.25rem">
      <div style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px">CX Insights</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.76rem;color:var(--text-2);margin-bottom:1rem">Anonymized data from 247 diners across 12 restaurant partners.</div>
