 no bread. A satisfying, fully gluten-free alternative.',tags:['✅ No bread · naturally GF','🥩 Cured meats & veg','🫒 Marinated olives included'],tagTypes:['free','note','note']}}},{chicken:{any:{dish:'Crispy Chicken Sandwich',emoji:'🍗',desc:'Order the crispy chicken sandwich — a fried chicken breast in a brioche bun with lettuce, pickles, and sriracha mayo. If it\'s not on the menu, the kitchen can usually build one from the chicken tender basket.',tags:['🍔 Served in brioche bun','🌶️ Ask for mild or spicy','🌾 Contains gluten'],tagTypes:['note','note','warn']},gf:{dish:'Grilled Chicken + Loaded Potato Skins',emoji:'🍗',desc:'Skip the battered chicken and go for a grilled chicken breast — ask your server if they can plate it simply with seasoning and a side of loaded potato skins, which are naturally gluten-free.',tags:['✅ GF-friendly combo','🥔 Potato skins are naturally GF','🔥 Ask for grilled not fried'],tagTypes:['free','free','note']}},seafood:{any:{dish:'Fish & Chips',emoji:'🐟',desc:'The pub classic — battered cod or haddock fillet with thick-cut chips, mushy peas, and tartar sauce. Ask your server what fish is fresh today. A squeeze of malt vinegar is non-negotiable.',tags:['🐟 Beer-battered fish','🌾 Contains gluten (batter)','🍟 Served with chips'],tagTypes:['note','warn','note']},gf:{dish:'Grilled Salmon + Southwest Salad',emoji:'🐟',desc:'Ask the kitchen for a grilled salmon fillet instead of battered fish. Pair it with the Southwest salad minus the tortilla strips for a fully gluten-free, high-protein pub meal.',tags:['✅ Ask for GF grilled salmon','🥗 Southwest salad, no strips','🌾 Skip the batter entirely'],tagTypes:['free','free','note']}},sandwich:{any:{dish:'The Crown Classic Smash Burger',emoji:'🥪',desc:'The smash burger is the move — two smashed patties, American cheese, pickles, and Thousand Island in a toasted brioche bun. Ask for extra pickles. Add bacon for $2.',tags:['🍔 Double smash patty','🥒 Extra pickles recommended','🌾 Brioche bun contains gluten'],tagTypes:['note','note','warn']},gf:{dish:'Smash Burger in Lettuce Wrap',emoji:'🥪',desc:'Get the smash burger but swap the brioche bun for a crispy lettuce wrap — most pub kitchens do this no problem. Same great patty, cheese, pickles, and sauce, just without the gluten.',tags:['✅ Lettuce wrap = GF','🥬 Iceberg wrap holds up well','🧀 Cheese & sauce are GF'],tagTypes:['free','note','note']}}},{chicken:{any:{dish:'Poulet Rôti aux Herbes',emoji:'🍗',desc:'Ask your server if there\'s a roast chicken or chicken supreme available — French bistros almost always have one. Expect it with a Dijon cream sauce, roasted potatoes, and tarragon.',tags:['🐓 Roast or pan-seared','🥛 Cream sauce (contains dairy)','🍷 Often served with wine sauce'],tagTypes:['note','warn','note']},gf:{dish:'Chicken Supreme, No Roux Sauce',emoji:'🍗',desc:'Order the chicken but ask your server to hold the flour-thickened sauce — request a simple butter and herb jus instead, which is GF. Pair with the heritage carrots or a green salad on the side.',tags:['✅ GF with sauce swap','🧈 Butter jus instead of roux','🥕 Heritage carrots on the side'],tagTypes:['free','note','note']}},seafood:{any:{dish:'Sole Meunière ou Saumon Grillé',emoji:'🐟',desc:'Ask about the fish of the day — French bistros rotate seasonal fish dishes. Sole meunière (pan-fried in butter and lemon) or a simply grilled salmon with beurre blanc are beautiful choices.',tags:['🐟 Ask for the catch of the day','🧈 Butter sauce (dairy)','🍋 Light and elegant'],tagTypes:['note','warn','note']},gf:{dish:'Grilled Sole or Salmon + Simple Salad',emoji:'🐟',desc:'Ask for fish grilled simply in butter and lemon — sole meunière without the flour dredge is naturally GF. Pair with a green salad dressed in vinaigrette. Avoid any sauce described as "velouté".',tags:['✅ Ask for no flour dredge','🚫 Avoid velouté sauces','🥗 Green salad pairs perfectly'],tagTypes:['free','warn','note']}},sandwich:{any:{dish:'Croque Monsieur',emoji:'🥪',desc:'A proper French bistro will have a Croque Monsieur — toasted country bread with ham and Gruyère, topped with a béchamel sauce and broiled until golden. Rich, indulgent, and very French.',tags:['🧀 Gruyère + béchamel','🥖 Country bread (contains gluten)','🍖 Ham (pork)'],tagTypes:['warn','warn','note']},gf:{dish:'Charcuterie & Crudités Plate',emoji:'🧀',desc:'French bistros rarely have GF bread. Ask instead for a charcuterie plate — cured duck, cornichons, Dijon mustard, and seasonal crudités. Ask your server to hold the croûtons and bread.',tags:['✅ No bread version available','🦆 Cured duck & meats','🥒 Cornichons & crudités'],tagTypes:['free','note','note']}}}];

// STATE
let currentVenue=0,currentItem=0,activeMood=null,gfMode=false,isPlaying=false;
let utterance=null,wordSpans=[],fontStep=2;
const fontSteps=['XS','S','M','L','XL'],fontSizes=['0.78rem','0.85rem','0.92rem','1.05rem','1.18rem'];

// TAB SWITCHING
function switchMainTab(tab,btn){
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-pill').forEach(p=>p.classList.remove('active'));
  btn.classList.add('active');
  const map={demo:'tab-demo',workflow:'tab-workflow',analytics:'tab-analytics-left'};
  ['tab-demo','tab-workflow','tab-analytics-left'].forEach(id=>document.getElementById(id).style.display=id===map[tab]?'':'none');
}

function switchMobile(which){
  ['mTabHome','mTabMenu','mTabStats'].forEach(id=>document.getElementById(id).classList.remove('active'));
  ['colLeft','colMain','colRight'].forEach(id=>document.getElementById(id).classList.remove('mob-active'));
  if(which==='home'){document.getElementById('mTabHome').classList.add('active');document.getElementById('colLeft').classList.add('mob-active');}
  if(which==='menu'){document.getElementById('mTabMenu').classList.add('active');document.getElementById('colMain').classList.add('mob-active');}
  if(which==='stats'){document.getElementById('mTabStats').classList.add('active');document.getElementById('colRight').classList.add('mob-active');}
}

// VENUE
function switchVenue(idx,btn){
  currentVenue=idx;currentItem=0;
  document.querySelectorAll('.venue-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));
  btn.classList.add('active');
  stopAudio();clearMood();
  const card=document.getElementById('venueIntelCard');
  document.getElementById('venueThinking').style.display='flex';
  card.style.display='none';
  setTimeout(()=>{
    const v=venues[idx];
    document.getElementById('venueHeroBg').className='venue-intel-hero '+v.theme;
    document.getElementById('venueIcon').textContent=v.emoji;
    document.getElementById('venueName').textContent=v.name;
    document.getElementById('venueType').textContent=v.type;
    document.getElementById('venueSummary').innerHTML=v.summary;
    document.getElementById('venueTags').innerHTML=v.tags.map(t=>`<span class="venue-tag">${t}</span>`).join('');
    document.getElementById('restaurantName').textContent=v.name;
    document.getElementById('menuHeader').className=v.theme+' menu-display-header';
    rebuildChips();loadItem(0);updateVenueGfAlert();
    if(gfMode)renderGFBanner();
    document.getElementById('venueThinking').style.display='none';
    card.style.display='';
  },600);
}

function rebuildChips(){
  document.getElementById('menuChips').innerHTML=venues[currentVenue].items.map((it,i)=>
    `<button class="menu-chip${i===0?' active':''}" onclick="selectItem(${i},this)">${it.emoji} ${it.name.split(' ').slice(0,3).join(' ')}</button>`
  ).join('');
}

function loadItem(idx){
  const item=venues[currentVenue].items[idx];
  document.getElementById('itemName').textContent=item.name;
  document.getElementById('itemPrice').textContent=item.price;
  document.getElementById('itemDesc').textContent=item.desc;
  document.getElementById('menuCatLabel').textContent=item.category;
  hideResult();
  document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='Awaiting request…';
}

function selectItem(idx,btn){
  currentItem=idx;
  document.querySelectorAll('.menu-chip').forEach(c=>c.classList.remove('active'));
  btn.classList.add('active');
  loadItem(idx);
  if(gfMode)renderGFBanner();
}

// DISPLAY SETTINGS
function toggleDyslexia(btn){
  btn.classList.toggle('on');
  document.getElementById('menuItemBox').classList.toggle('dyslexia',btn.classList.contains('on'));
}

function toggleHighlight(btn){
  const on=btn.classList.contains('on');
  document.querySelectorAll('#itemDesc,#resultDesc').forEach(el=>{
    el.style.background=on?'linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,149,0,0.08) 0%,transparent 100%)':'';
  });
}

function toggleGlutenFree(btn){
  btn.classList.toggle('on');
  gfMode=btn.classList.contains('on');
  const banner=document.getElementById('gfBanner');
  if(gfMode){renderGFBanner();banner.style.display='block';updateVenueGfAlert();}
  else{banner.style.display='none';document.getElementById('venueGfAlert').style.display='none';}
  if(activeMood){const ab=document.querySelector('.mood-btn.active');if(ab)selectMood(activeMood,ab);}
}

function updateVenueGfAlert(){
  const el=document.getElementById('venueGfAlert');
  if(gfMode){
    el.style.display='block';
    el.textContent=venues[currentVenue].gfWarning;
    el.className='venue-gf-alert '+(venues[currentVenue].id==='pub'?'caution':'unsafe');
  } else {el.style.display='none';}
}

function renderGFBanner(){
  const gfData=venues[currentVenue].gfStatus[currentItem];
  const inner=document.getElementById('gfBannerInner');
  inner.className='gf-banner '+gfData.status;
  const recHtml=gfData.recs.map(i=>{
    const it=venues[currentVenue].items[i];
    return `<button class="gf-rec-chip" onclick="jumpToItem(${i})">${it.emoji} ${it.name.split(' ').slice(0,3).join(' ')}…</button>`;
  }).join('');
  inner.innerHTML=`<div class="gf-banner-title">${gfData.icon} ${gfData.title}</div><div class="gf-banner-body">${gfData.msg}</div>${gfData.recs.length?`<div style="margin-top:6px;font-size:0.66rem;font-weight:700;opacity:0.75">GF-safe picks:</div><div class="gf-rec-chips">${recHtml}</div>`:''}`;
}

function jumpToItem(idx){
  currentItem=idx;
  document.querySelectorAll('.menu-chip').forEach((c,i)=>c.classList.toggle('active',i===idx));
  loadItem(idx);renderGFBanner();
}

function changeFontSize(dir){
  fontStep=Math.max(0,Math.min(4,fontStep+dir));
  document.getElementById('fontSizeDisplay').textContent=fontSteps[fontStep];
  document.getElementById('itemDesc').style.fontSize=fontSizes[fontStep];
}

// MOOD
function selectMood(mood,btn){
  if(activeMood===mood){clearMood();return;}
  activeMood=mood;
  document.querySelectorAll('.mood-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));
  btn.classList.add('active');
  const card=document.getElementById('recCard');
  card.classList.add('visible');
  document.getElementById('recDish').textContent='';
  document.getElementById('recDesc').textContent='';
  document.getElementById('recTags').innerHTML='';
  document.getElementById('recEmoji').textContent=mood==='chicken'?'🍗':mood==='seafood'?'🐟':'🥪';
  document.getElementById('recLabel').textContent='Finding the best match…';
  document.getElementById('recThinking').style.display='flex';
  const rec=moodRecs[currentVenue][mood][gfMode?'gf':'any'];
  const prompt=`You are a friendly restaurant concierge. The restaurant is: ${venues[currentVenue].name} (${venues[currentVenue].type}). The diner wants: ${mood}.${gfMode?' They are strictly gluten-free.':''} Give a warm, conversational recommendation in 3 short plain sentences (max 12 words each). Suggest a specific dish or combination. Be practical — if the exact dish isn't guaranteed on the menu, say what to ask the server. No jargon. No preamble. Just the recommendation.`;
  setTimeout(()=>{
    callClaude(prompt,text=>{
      document.getElementById('recThinking').style.display='none';
      document.getElementById('recEmoji').textContent=rec.emoji;
      document.getElementById('recLabel').textContent=gfMode?'🌾 GF Pick for You':'⭐ Our Pick for You';
      document.getElementById('recDish').textContent=rec.dish;
      document.getElementById('recDesc').textContent=text||rec.desc;
      document.getElementById('recTags').innerHTML=rec.tags.map((t,i)=>`<span class="rec-tag ${rec.tagTypes[i]==='free'?'tag-free':rec.tagTypes[i]==='warn'?'tag-warn':'tag-note'}">${t}</span>`).join('');
    });
  },700);
}

function clearMood(){
  activeMood=null;
  document.querySelectorAll('.mood-btn').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));
  document.getElementById('recCard').classList.remove('visible');
  document.getElementById('recThinking').style.display='none';
}

// AI ACTIONS
function showThinking(msg){
  document.getElementById('aiPlaceholder').style.display='none';
  document.getElementById('aiResult').classList.remove('visible');
  const t=document.getElementById('aiThinking');
  t.classList.add('visible');
  document.getElementById('thinkingText').textContent=msg;
}

function hideResult(){
  document.getElementById('aiResult').classList.remove('visible');
  document.getElementById('aiPlaceholder').style.display='flex';
  document.getElementById('aiThinking').classList.remove('visible');
  stopAudio();
}

function showResult(name,price,desc,allergens){
  document.getElementById('aiThinking').classList.remove('visible');
  document.getElementById('aiPlaceholder').style.display='none';
  document.getElementById('resultName').textContent=name;
  document.getElementById('resultPrice').textContent=price||venues[currentVenue].items[currentItem].price;
  const descEl=document.getElementById('resultDesc');
  wordSpans=[];
  descEl.innerHTML=desc.split(' ').map((w,i)=>`<span class="rword" data-i="${i}">${w} </span>`).join('');
  wordSpans=Array.from(descEl.querySelectorAll('.rword'));
  const row=document.getElementById('allergenRow');
  row.innerHTML='';
  if(allergens)allergens.forEach(a=>{
    const tag=document.createElement('span');
    tag.className='allergen-tag '+(a.type==='free'?'free':'warn');
    tag.textContent=a.label;row.appendChild(tag);
  });
  document.getElementById('aiResult').classList.add('visible');
  if(document.getElementById('autoPlayCheck').checked)setTimeout(()=>startAudio(),300);
}

function callClaude(prompt,onSuccess){
  fetch('https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({model:'claude-sonnet-4-20250514',max_tokens:1000,messages:[{role:'user',content:prompt}]})})
  .then(r=>r.json()).then(data=>{const text=data.content?.map(b=>b.text||'').join('')||'';onSuccess(text);})
  .catch(()=>onSuccess(null));
}

function simplifyMenu(){
  document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='Simplifying menu language…';
  showThinking('Rewriting in plain English for dyslexic readers…');
  const item=venues[currentVenue].items[currentItem];
  const gfNote=gfMode?' The user is gluten-free — note if this dish is safe or suggest a swap.':'';
  const prompt=`You are an accessibility specialist helping dyslexic diners understand restaurant menus. Rewrite this menu item in plain, simple English. Use short sentences (max 10 words each). Avoid culinary jargon. Keep it warm and appetizing. Max 4 sentences total.${gfNote}\nMenu item: "${item.name}" - ${item.desc}\nRespond with ONLY the simplified description, nothing else.`;
  setTimeout(()=>callClaude(prompt,text=>{const s=simplifications[currentVenue][currentItem];document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='✦ Simplified — Plain English';showResult(s.name,null,text||s.desc,s.allergens);}),900);
}

function checkAllergens(){
  document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='Checking allergens…';
  showThinking('Scanning for allergens and dietary information…');
  const item=venues[currentVenue].items[currentItem];
  const gfNote=gfMode?' Also clearly state whether this dish is gluten-free or not.':'';
  const prompt=`You are a food safety expert. Analyze this menu item and list all allergens clearly and simply.\nMenu item: "${item.name}" - ${item.desc}\nReply in 2-3 short plain sentences. Start with "Contains:" then list allergens. Then "Safe from:" and list what's absent. Max 40 words.${gfNote}`;
  setTimeout(()=>callClaude(prompt,text=>{const a=allergenChecks[currentVenue][currentItem];const s=simplifications[currentVenue][currentItem];document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='⚠ Allergen Summary';showResult(a.name,null,text||a.desc,s.allergens);}),1100);
}

function translateSimple(){
  document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='Translating to plain English…';
  showThinking('Converting culinary language to everyday words…');
  const item=venues[currentVenue].items[currentItem];
  const prompt=`You are helping someone with dyslexia understand what they would actually receive if they ordered this dish. Explain it in 3-4 very short, plain sentences as if talking to a friend. No jargon whatsoever.\nMenu item: "${item.name}" - ${item.desc}\nStart with "What you're getting:" then explain. Max 50 words.`;
  setTimeout(()=>callClaude(prompt,text=>{const p=plainEnglish[currentVenue][currentItem];document.getElementById('aiOutputTitle').textContent='🌍 Plain English Explanation';showResult(p.name,null,text||p.desc,null);}),800);
}

// AUDIO
function toggleAudio(){isPlaying?stopAudio():startAudio();}

function startAudio(){
  const descEl=document.getElementById('resultDesc');
  const name=document.getElementById('resultName').textContent;
  const fullText=name+'. '+descEl.textContent;
  stopAudio();
  if('speechSynthesis' in window){
    utterance=new SpeechSynthesisUtterance(fullText);
    utterance.rate=0.82;utterance.pitch=1.05;
    utterance.onboundary=e=>{
      if(e.name!=='word')return;
      wordSpans.forEach(s=>s.classList.remove('lit'));
      const textSoFar=fullText.substring(0,e.charIndex);
      const wIdx=textSoFar.trim().split(/\s+/).length-1-name.split(' ').length-1;
      if(wIdx>=0&&wIdx<wordSpans.length){wordSpans[wIdx].classList.add('lit');wordSpans[wIdx].scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'nearest'});}
    };
    utterance.onend=()=>{wordSpans.forEach(s=>s.classList.remove('lit'));stopAudio();};
    window.speechSynthesis.speak(utterance);
  }
  isPlaying=true;
  document.getElementById('playBtn').textContent='⏸';
  document.getElementById('waveform').classList.add('playing');
  document.getElementById('audioLabel').textContent='Reading aloud…';
}

function stopAudio(){
  if('speechSynthesis' in window)window.speechSynthesis.cancel();
  wordSpans.forEach(s=>s.classList.remove('lit'));
  isPlaying=false;
  const btn=document.getElementById('playBtn');if(btn)btn.textContent='▶';
  const wf=document.getElementById('waveform');if(wf)wf.classList.remove('playing');
  const lbl=document.getElementById('audioLabel');if(lbl)lbl.textContent='Read aloud';
}

// INIT
window.addEventListener('load',()=>{
  const vals=['1,284','−41%','4.7','−38%'];
  ['kpi1','kpi2','kpi3','kpi4'].forEach((id,i)=>{
    const el=document.getElementById(id);el.textContent='…';
    setTimeout(()=>el.textContent=vals[i],400+i*150);
  });
  document.getElementById('menuItemBox').classList.add('dyslexia');
});
</script>
